PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1994-1282 of July 22, 1994 which appointed REID MORDEN as President and Chief Executive Officer of Atomic Energy of Canada Limited, by revoking the words "for a term of three years" and substituting the words "for a term ending December 31, 1997".
